<HEADLINE> OAU Head Pays Working Visit to Congo (K) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, March 31 (Xinhua) -- Secretary-general of the
Organization of African Unity (OAU), Salim Ahmed Salim, left here
Wednesday for Kinshasa for a working visit to the Democratic
Republic of Congo (DRC).
</P>
<P>
An OAU press release issued here said that during his stay in
Kinshasa from Wednesday to Friday, the secretary-general is
expected to meet and hold discussions with DRC President Laurent
Kabila.
