Salim said that the OAU had been playing an active role in
support of regional efforts aimed at seeking a lasting and
peaceful solution to the conflict there.
</P>
<P>
He noted that the Southern African Development Community
(SADC), the OAU, the United Nations and the countries in the
region, need to redouble their efforts in order to end this tragic
conflict and to do so on the basis of the fundamental principles
of the U.N. and the OAU. 
