</P>
<P>
Protestants demand that the Irish Republican Army disarm
before its political ally Sinn Fein can take part in a new
Catholic-Protestant coalition cabinet. The row over the
disarmament has posed a major stumbling block in the peace
agreement to be fully implemented. 
