involved in rape cases of minors, he said.
</P>
<P>
"Violence against children, like kidnapping, have gone up so
much that often we feel ashamed to think that we are living in the
country's capital," seven-year-old Jagdeep said.
</P>
<P>
Noted sportsmen, some MPs and Congress party leader H. K. L.
Bhagat also took part in the demonstration. 
