during the trial opening, the organizers have added more toilets
and chairs. Some 400,000 trees and shrubs have been planted at the
site and a large number of flower pots and lawns are in place.
</P>
<P>
The display has 112 endangered or rare plant species that have
been listed under state protection in China, the organizers say.
</P>
<P>
Officials and experts from the construction and agriculture
ministries and the State Forestry Administration have visited
Kunming to oversee the preparatory work and have made suggestions.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
