refugees to the maximum.
</P>
<P>
An European Union (EU) delegation led by State Minister of
German Foreign Ministry Gunter Verheugen and EU Commissioner for
Humanitarian Affairs Emma Bonino visited Albania and Macedonia on
Wednesday, preparing to help shelter the refugees.
</P>
<P>
The exodus of refugees from Kosovo came as a result of NATO
airstrikes on Yugoslavia that started on March 24. 
