discussions over decommissioning in Northern Ireland on Wednesday
had produced movement toward a deal.
</P>
<P>
"We believe good progress has been made here but there is still
more to do," he said before leaving Belfast early in the afternoon.
(Blair-Irish-Talks)
</P>
